1
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,060
I've memorized it all.

2
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,880
The First Prince has a very strange temper.

3
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,560
He hasn't been close to any women since he entered the palace.

4
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,880
How long you can survive

5
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,079
depends on your luck.

6
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:22,490
Aunt Huixin,

7
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,820
why are you here again?

8
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,079
Her Highness cares about you, Your Highness,

9
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,720
so she specially picked a clever maid for you.

10
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,400
Her Highness chose her personally this time.

11
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,000
You absolutely cannot refuse.

12
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,880
How many people have been sent here in total?

13
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:34,000
His Highness has already said

14
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,000
he doesn't want others to serve him.

15
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:39,120
Many thanks to Her Highness for her kindness.

16
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,880
I've told Consort Yu before,

17
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,800
don't send anyone else here.

18
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,240
Please take her back.

19
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,560
I

20
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,370
greet the First Prince.

21
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,320
Since it is Consort Yu's intention,

22
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:03,600
then she can stay.

23
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:04,700
You see,

24
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,360
I told you.

25
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,880
Chosen by Her Highness personally,

26
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,760
His Highness will definitely be satisfied.

27
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,690
Thank you, Aunt,

28
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,800
for thanking Consort Yu on my behalf.

29
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,160
If Her Highness knows that Your Highness

30
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,600
appreciates her intentions,

31
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,800
she will definitely be happy.

32
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,200
Then I will take my leave.

33
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:28,250
My family and I originally came to Nanping for business.

34
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,810
We opened a small workshop.

35
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:32,200
But since we are new here,

36
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,840
it's really not easy to gain a foothold in the capital.

37
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,560
I heard

38
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,740
the palace was recruiting maids.

39
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,840
I thought

40
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:41,720
I could drum up some business in the palace.

41
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:44,440
But for a small workshop like ours,

42
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:48,140
how could we have the chance to interact with the royal palace?

43
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,760
You are quite calculating.

44
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,970
But in the royal palace,

45
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,900
there are special weaving rooms.

46
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:58,800
Even if there's a need to buy ready-made clothes and fabrics,

47
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,060
it has to go through layers of screening.

48
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,760
A lowly maid like you,

49
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:05,130
how can you influence that?

50
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,560
Your Highness makes a valid point.

51
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,240
So,

52
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,760
that is not my goal.

53
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:14,340
In this palace, besides the princes and ministers,

54
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,690
the most abundant are maids and servants.

55
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,079
Although they have a lowly status,

56
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:21,320
they have been working in the palace for years

57
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:23,880
and are also particular about their clothing.

58
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,600
If most of them

59
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,040
come to buy my fabric,

60
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,040
then

61
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:31,660
it's enough to support us in gaining a foothold in the capital.

62
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,900
Are you telling the truth?

63
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,200
I

64
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:45,140
would not dare to deceive Your Highness.

65
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,740
But as far as I know,

66
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:53,240
to apply for this maid position,

67
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,500
there must be a condition.

68
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,200
That is,

69
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,130
a household registration in Nanping.

70
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,080
Forgive my bluntness,

71
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:07,720
there's nothing that money can't do.

72
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,200
Your Highness,

73
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,920
do you have any other questions?

74
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:20,680
No.

75
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,160
You may step down.

76
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,040
Yes.

77
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,160
She looks quite unique.

78
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,980
Between her brows,

79
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,400
she somewhat resembles my late sister.

80
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,220
Your Highness.

81
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,040
You stay.

82
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,000
The rest of you may leave.

83
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:33,159
What is your name?

84
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,320
I am

85
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:37,960
Liu Xu.

86
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:48,120
Liu Xu, 17 years old.

87
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,400
A registered resident of Nanping Township, Nanping Prefecture.

88
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,280
Unmarried.

89
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,080
Three people in the household.

90
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:54,000
One male

91
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,400
and two females.

92
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,960
If you are Liu Xu,

93
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,440
then who is this?

94
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,360
What you committed today

95
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,800
is the crime of deceiving the emperor.

96
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,720
Not only you,

97
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,440
but the family of three listed here

98
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,520
must all die.

99
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:25,210
Please spare them, Your Highness.

100
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,680
I originally migrated from the border.

101
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,060
Unexpectedly,

102
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:36,320
my parents and brother encountered bandits

103
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:38,120
and unfortunately passed away.

104
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,280
So I fled all the way here,

105
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,640
thinking that if I could be a maid in the palace,

106
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,840
I would never have to suffer from cold and hunger again.

107
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,600
But

108
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,960
I don't have a Nanping household registration,

109
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:52,920
so I had no choice but to do this.

110
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,800
Please spare my life, Your Highness.

111
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,720
I did not mean to deceive you.

112
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,360
Your words

113
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,160
have actually moved me.

114
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:11,480
I also quite like your looks.

115
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:15,440
And I happen to need a clever girl by my side.

116
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,680
Very well.

117
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:20,360
I will give you a chance.

118
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,740
Thank you, Your Highness.

119
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,000
You've been talking for so long,

120
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,240
you must be thirsty.

121
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:36,960
Drink it.

122
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,280
If you don't want to stay, you may leave.

123
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:48,160
I won't force you.

124
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,920
I snuck in so smoothly,

125
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:58,340
and was assigned to the lazy First Prince's palace.

126
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:01,260
I didn't expect to be schemed against by Consort Yu.

127
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,160
No.

128
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,800
My plan

129
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,160
cannot fail here at the last minute.

130
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,600
Forgive my bluntness.

131
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,360
Your tea has a deep meaning, Your Highness.

132
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,760
But if I leave now,

133
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,360
I will still die.

134
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,360
I really like you more and more.

135
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:26,160
You truly are a clever and sweet girl.

136
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:30,360
I really want to spare your life.

137
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,120
Let's see if you can handle it.

138
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:39,000
Naturally, I hope to live a little longer.

139
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:26,240
I knew I wasn't wrong about you.

140
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,860
What is your real name?

141
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,080
I am

142
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,120
Ling Xuele.

143
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:36,200
Change Liu Xu on the roster to Ling Xuele.

144
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,500
I will do it right away.

145
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,780
If you obediently listen to me in the future,

146
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:52,330
I will ensure you live a long and safe life.

147
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,920
If you dare to plot against me,

148
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,480
within a month,

149
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,570
without me doing anything,

150
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:02,120
you will die of poisoning.

151
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:07,100
I am willing to pledge my loyalty to you unto death, Your Highness.

152
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:09,200
Father.

153
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:10,360
Mother.

154
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,610
Please forgive my reckless behavior.

155
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,600
For Xuecang,

156
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,010
I am willing to pay with my life.

157
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:21,660
Your Highness.

158
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,210
Come.

159
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,200
Tingfeng.

160
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:34,260
How many years have you served in the palace?

161
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,560
My family has been in the military for generations.

162
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:40,620
I entered the palace when I was young.

163
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:43,480
I suppose it's been about 7 or 8 years.

164
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,120
Then in your opinion,

165
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:49,360
Consort Yu has repeatedly shown me goodwill,

166
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,160
does she have other intentions?

167
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:55,700
Why do you suddenly mention Consort Yu, Your Highness?

168
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:58,520
We traveled all the way here from Linzhou City.

169
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,360
Now in this royal palace,

170
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:03,140
we are the only ones who know each other best.

171
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,410
If you are truly loyal to me,

172
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,410
speak your mind.

173
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,160
I swear,

174
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:14,650
I have no ulterior motives toward Your Highness.

175
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,120
However,

176
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:19,600
although I have served in the palace for a long time,

177
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,200
I have never paid attention to

178
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,600
the gossip in the palace.

179
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,920
Since Your Highness has asked,

180
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,680
I will boldly guess.

181
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,240
What Consort Yu did today,

182
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,160
I'm afraid,

183
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,280
is firstly a show of strength,

184
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:36,410
and secondly a test.

185
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:39,920
Come.

186
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:42,660
Your Highness.

187
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,560
It's my first day back in the palace.

188
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,920
Consort Yu knows my father has been fighting wars for years,

189
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:58,000
and ordered the palace to cut expenses

190
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,530
to subsidize military use.

191
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,080
Yet she sent me

192
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,680
so many extravagant things.

193
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,640
I returned them all.

194
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,960
But as for attendants and maids,

195
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,000
she keeps arranging them for me.

196
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,200
If I refuse again,

197
00:13:12,920 --> 00:13:15,180
I'm afraid it will arouse her suspicion.

198
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:16,680
Then,

199
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:19,560
does Your Highness think

200
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,890
that this girl Xue Le

201
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,650
was arranged by Consort Yu?

202
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,700
What are Emperor Yun's

203
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:43,520
usual hobbies?

204
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,260
Where does he usually appear?

205
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:50,080
I heard that after every morning court,

206
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,340
Emperor Yun goes to the Imperial Garden.

207
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:55,640
The Imperial Garden is located here in the palace.

208
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,660
There are 4 paths to get there.

209
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,220
What are you doing?

210
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:06,680
Your Highness has been sitting here for 2 hours.

211
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:08,480
I thought you were asleep.

212
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:14,880
Aunt Huixin.

213
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:20,450
Greetings, Your Highness.

214
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:24,360
Her Ladyship is considerate of your difficult adjustment to the palace,

215
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:26,880
so you don't need to pay your respects to her today.

216
00:15:26,880 --> 00:15:28,360
She also ordered me to bring you

217
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,560
some light pastries.

218
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,340
Her Ladyship also said

219
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,360
if Your Highness needs anything,

220
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,280
just ask.

221
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:38,540
If the maids don't serve you well,

222
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:40,280
we can send someone else.

223
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:43,740
Thank Consort Yu for her concern.

224
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,290
Yunchuan is doing fine.

225
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:47,480
Gong Zeyu.

226
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,500
Your Highness.

227
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:58,850
Come in quickly.

228
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,380
What happened to you, Your Highness?

229
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,650
It's just a flesh wound.

230
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:23,200
You don't need to use so much medicine.

231
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,400
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

232
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:27,080
Fortunately, the wound is not deep.

233
00:16:31,040 --> 00:16:33,320
The person we met outside the palace today

234
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:35,180
must have been sent by Consort Yu.

235
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,680
Does she want me dead that badly?

236
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:41,610
I actually underestimated Yunchuan.

237
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:43,160
As a prince,

238
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:46,600
he is secretive all day, leaving early and returning late.

239
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,880
I don't know what he does outside the palace.

240
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:51,340
Today he even came back covered in injuries.

241
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:52,520
Whatever.

242
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:54,200
As long as he doesn't pay attention to my whereabouts.
